question: Where can I find fast food restaurant as you head towards Bowery Gallery, New York, NY from Dealaman Nature Trail and Pond, Warren Township, NJ, within a radius of 60 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.506528 40.625648)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.004484 40.75132)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.506528 40.625648)',4326)::geography, 60000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.506528 40.625648)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
